 A rider in costumes cuts an apple as he performs during the 20th medieval festival of Ouffet in Ouffet, province of Liege, Belgium, on April 10, 2022. Highlighting performances, markets as well as various activities with the culture of the Middle Ages, the two-day festival attracted many visitors. (Xinhua/Zheng Huansong)  Visitors watch a fight performance during the 20th medieval festival of Ouffet in Ouffet, province of Liege, Belgium, on April 10, 2022. Highlighting performances, markets as well as various activities with the culture of the Middle Ages, the two-day festival attracted many visitors. (Xinhua/Zheng Huansong)  A fire breather performs during the 20th medieval festival of Ouffet in Ouffet, province of Liege, Belgium, on April 10, 2022. Highlighting performances, markets as well as various activities with the culture of the Middle Ages, the two-day festival attracted many visitors. (Xinhua/Zheng Huansong)  A rider in costumes performs during the 20th medieval festival of Ouffet in Ouffet, province of Liege, Belgium, on April 10, 2022. Highlighting performances, markets as well as various activities with the culture of the Middle Ages, the two-day festival attracted many visitors. (Xinhua/Zheng Huansong)